+ Class Properties

++ Public

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$backlink -- A link back to the previous page: list results, bookmarked page, etc.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$err -- An array of error messages.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$feed -- Feed information.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$formdata -- The current form processing object.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_base -- The <base> href value for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_bottom -- An array of content for the layout <div id="bottom"> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_left -- An array of content for the layout <div id="left"> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_link -- An array of <link> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_meta -- An array of <meta> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_object -- An array of <object> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_right -- An array of content for the layout <div id="right"> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_script -- An array of <script> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_style -- An array of <style> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_title -- The <title> tag value for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$layout_top -- An array of content for the layout <div id="top"> block.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$list -- The list of all bookmarks for the current page.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$order -- The requested bookmark order (subj, tags, created, etc).

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$owner_handle -- The current owner_handle being displayed.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$page -- The current page number being displayed.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$pages -- The total number of pages in the query.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$tags -- The tags requested for filtering results.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$tags_in_use -- The list of all tags in use by the current owner_handle.

++ Protected

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_action -- The action being requested of (performed by) the application.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_action_default -- The default controller action.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_action_info -- Pathinfo mappings for each controller action.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_bookmarks -- A bookmarks node interaction manager.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_config -- User-defined configuration values.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_dir -- Base directory under which actions, views, etc. are located.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_info -- Application request parameters collected from the URI pathinfo.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_layout -- The name of the layout to use for the view, minus the .layout.php suffix.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_layout_dir -- Where the layout directory is located.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_layout_var -- The name of the variable where page content is placed in the layout.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_name -- The short-name of this application.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_query -- Application request parameters collected from the URI query string.

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_user -- Local reference to the 'user' object in Solar::registry().

* Solar_App_Bookmarks::$_view -- The name of the view to be rendered after the action, minus the .view.php suffix.

